## Dashboard Summary

### 🏠 Home
Acts as the landing page of the workbook with project details, navigation buttons, and last refresh information.

### 📈 Executive Dashboard
Provides an overall business performance summary using key KPIs and sales trends.

### 👥 Customer & Sales Dashboard
Analyzes customer behavior, customer segments, top customers, and sales trends.

### 📦 Product Analysis Dashboard
Shows product performance, category-wise sales, sub-category analysis, and top-performing products.

### 🌍 Regional Analysis Dashboard
Compares sales and profit across different regions and markets to identify the best-performing locations.

### 💰 Profitability Dashboard
Focuses on profit analysis by category, region, segment, and monthly profit trends.


