## Outcome

This Excel dashboard converts raw sales data into an interactive Business Intelligence report. It provides a clear view of business performance across different areas and helps in analyzing sales, customers, products, regions, and profitability. Since the dashboard is connected directly to the MySQL database, it can be refreshed anytime with a single click.
